title: CANT LAUNCH LEAGUE
body:
I PRESS LAUNCH BUT THEN IT GIVES ME AN ERROR MESSAGE SAYING THAT THE APP CANT START PROPERLY

WHAT CAN BE DONE??

replies.body: There may be a security setting that's blocking your patcher from launching.  Try the steps out in the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide to help, making sure to go over each instruction to rule out possibilities.  I hope that helps!
